General.Name: Harboes Bryggeri A/S
General.Description: Harboes Bryggeri A/S develops, produces, and markets beverages and malt-based food ingredients worldwide. It offers beer, energy drink, malt beverage, and soda under the Harboe, Caribia, Mecklenburger, Bear Beer, Darguner, Hyper Malt, Viiking, and XRAY brands. Harboes Bryggeri A/S was founded in 1883 and is based in Skælskør, Denmark.
